{"word":"H3807 - כָּתַת - kâthath - kaw-thath' - Beat","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">כָּתַת</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong>kâthath"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong>kaw-thath'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong>Beat"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - மடங்கடி, நசுக்கு, தகர், முறியடி, இடி, அடி, அழி, நொறுக்கு"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"to beat, to crush by beating, to crush to pieces, to crush fine"},{"paragraph":"a) (Qal)"},{"paragraph":"1) to beat or crush fine"},{"paragraph":"2) to beat, to hammer"},{"paragraph":"b) (Piel)"},{"paragraph":"1) to beat or to crush fine"},{"paragraph":"2) to beat, to hammer"},{"paragraph":"c) (Pual) to be beaten"},{"paragraph":"d) (Hiphil) to beat in pieces, to shatter"},{"paragraph":"e) (Hophal) to be beaten, to be crushed"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>Part(s) of speech:</strong> Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English:</strong> A primitive root; to <i>bruise</i> or violently <i>strike: - </i>beat (down, to pieces), break in pieces, crushed, destroy, discomfit, smite, stamp."},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H3795 - כָּתִית - kâthîyth - kaw-theeth'/3795\">H3795</a>, <a href=\"#/H3807 - כָּתַת - kâthath - kaw-thath'/3807\">H3807</a>, <a href=\"#/H4386 - מְכִתָּה - mᵉkittâh - mek-it-taw'/4386\">H4386</a>"}]}